Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:38.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,Why are you working for evil, with your level of skills?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:42.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,Lord Hanzō is my clan. For the obligation! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Why are you hesitating?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:55.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Why do you live in shadows? Wouldn't you like to practice swordsmanship under the sun like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'd be doing that if I could! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:18.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,Onihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:21.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:31.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am a human too. I wanted to have a fight with you, Kojirō, for once, under the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Onihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Onihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's as far as you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:49.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Give it up-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:53.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jiraiyan! You're being slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,Lord Hanzō!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jiraiyan! Guide them to the other world! Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:05.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:10.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Feel the might of the chain of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,Baiken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:29.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Baiken! You came for us-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:34.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Without you, Musashi, Jipangu Martial Arts Competition won't be interesting as now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:46.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,There must be a power room, to operate a stronghold this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,So destroying that will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:54.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Senhime! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:01.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's full of scary traps...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:14.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Senhime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,You two should better become a skewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ushiwaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:45.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,It seems that we must be prepared for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,I won't. I believe in Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:53.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,More specifically, the friendship between Musashi's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:56.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Osenchan!\N-Mr. Ushiwaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Osenchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,So Musashi's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Lord Hanzō!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:12.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh, Jiraiyan, were you safe? You are truly the best of my Four Kings. Good job, good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:20.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's with your grim face? We will take those Musashi bunch down and dominate over the globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,Osenchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:25.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Musashi!\N-Kojirō!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:27.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Anything from that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:29.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,None-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,They already ran away, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shh! I can hear Osenchan's flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:39.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,This way-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:57.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Musashi... Kojirō... I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hanzō! Where is Osenchan-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:08.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Come here. Then you'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:10.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, you can't get away-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Go! Jiraiyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:25.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,Senhime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:27.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's a good thing that I believed in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Senhime is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hearing that is very relieving-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:44.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hanzō! When did you escape?! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:49.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,Open the door, Hanzō!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,A time bomb will soon explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:53.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:54.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,Lord Hanzō!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:59.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jiraiyan, guide them to the other world properly this time. Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:06.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō, get out of my way-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:15.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn, it's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:16.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jiraiyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:28.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,It should open by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Alright! We'll scrum by three this time-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:31.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:35.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,Again-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:59.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hanzō! There's nowhere for you to escape anymore! Disembowel and your death will be honorary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:03.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,You must be ignorant of the fact that I, Hanzō, am immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:07.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will turn over Jipangu State and take the world into my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:09.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,We found you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,You won't be doing as you want anymore-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:17.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Senhime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! I've been worried for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Your ambition ends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,Give it up, Hanzō!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:26.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,You were alive! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,I helped them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:33.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jiraiyan! You betrayed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:38.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,We have lost to the teamwork and friendship of Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,Save your honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:44.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Silence, you traitor! Fall into hell with the stronghold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:19:58.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,No! Everyone, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:39.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are all of you okay-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yeah, seems so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's great-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jiraiyan, you're safe-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:58.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Cut me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:03.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am a bad guy. I've betrayed my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:06.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,Even for a fag end of swordsman, I will know my shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:07.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jiraiyan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:15.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kerokichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:18.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jiraiyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:23.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,You can die whenever you want, but then what about Kerokichi-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:31.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jiraiyan! You're alive, so please keep being alive! For Kerokichi, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:36.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,There's someone who needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:39.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's enough, Jiraiyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:40.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:42.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Take a good care of Kerokichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:45.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! I'll skip my gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:48.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Gratitude, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:49.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:52.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,You have good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:54.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,Jiraiyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will pay back this favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:06.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,Take care-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:07.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,The blood-freezing battle at Karakuri Stronghold is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:18.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Something hot is gushing out from Musashi's heart, thanking the comrades who fought for the friendship despite of rivalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:23.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,But is Hanzō truly dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:43.70,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Sometimes the moon jumps over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:46.95,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,the pocket of empty sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:49.33,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Laugh loudly and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:51.95,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,morning will come tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:57.29,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much about losing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:00.88,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Keep going! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:03.30,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,A bare hand is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:13.39,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:21.44,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how life is! Look, a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:26.15,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,follows us wagging its tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:37.08,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:45.55,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how the future is, too! Look, tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.79,0:23:51.39,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,is opening its hands and smiling at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:09.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,General Ieyasu called us home, and we went back to Edotopia-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.16,0:24:12.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Being relaxed after a long time feels so good-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.37,0:24:15.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō is watching plays, and I'm at a temple festival with Zenigatan boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.92,0:24:19.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Osenchan was enjoying her marriage mettings and short holidays,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.21,0:24:21.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?! That Hanzō was still alive-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.97,0:24:24.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,Next story! The Most Evil! Hanzō Revives
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.00,0:24:27.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's stormy Edotopia-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
